FarmerType - Unnamed Package中的类
This class represents a farmer type, which has a name, levelRequirement which stores the level requirement needed to upgrade to this farmer type, bonusProduceEarnings which stores the bonus amount that can be earned, seedCostReduction which stores the cost reduction to buy seeds, waterBonusIncrease which stores the limit increase of water that can be received by the crop, fertilizerBonusIncrease which stores the the limit increase of fertilizer that can be received by the crop, and registrationFee which stores the amount needed to register for the farmer tier.
FarmerType(String, int, int, int, int, int, int) - 类的构造器 FarmerType
Creates a FarmerType object by supplying the name, levelRequirement, bonusProduceEarnings, seedCostReduction, waterBonusIncrease, fertilizerBonusIncrease, and registrationFee.
